# ==============================================================================
# Chronos - AI Context Ignore List
# ==============================================================================

# 1. Rust Build Artifacts
# The AI never needs to read compiled binaries or dependency object files.
target/
Cargo.lock

# 2. Database & Persistent Storage
# Prevent the AI from trying to parse raw binary database files or WAL logs.
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

# 3. SQLx Cached Metadata
# sqlx generates massive JSON files for offline compilation. These pollute the AI context.
.sqlx/

# 4. Captured Media & Ring Buffers
# The AI should not attempt to read the raw PNG/JPEG frames captured by the daemon.
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
captures/
frames/

# 5. Coverage & CI Reports
# We already set this up; the AI doesn't need to read the raw LCOV metric data.
lcov.info
coverage/

# 6. Environment & Secrets
# Keep local API keys and configurations out of the AI's memory.
.env
*.env
.env.*

# 7. Version Control
.git/